== Spell Strategy ==

=== Early Game (Levels 1-10) ===

* Heal is essential for survival
* Hurt saves HP vs high-defense enemies
* Sleep provides free turns

=== Mid Game (Levels 10-17) ===

* Stopspell counters enemy casters
* Outside saves time in dungeons
* Return enables efficient farming

=== Late Game (Levels 17-30) ===

* Healmore is primary healing
* Hurtmore damages any enemy efficiently
* Repel speeds up travel

=== Dragonlord Strategy ===

# Human form: Cast Stopspell, attack
# Dragon form: Alternate Hurtmore and Healmore

